Beyond convention.
 




Unique perspectives. Uncommon insight.
Differentiated strategies.
Salient offers a comprehensive suite of strategies that span master limited partnerships (MLPs), real estate, public and private equity, fixed income, credit and managed futures. Institutions and investment advisors use this platform to build smarter, more efficient portfolios.






People
Located in Houston, San Francisco, New York and Newport Beach, Salient’s team has distinct academic and industry-related backgrounds, offering unique perspectives across asset classes and global markets.


Read more






Perspective
Today’s markets require an investment approach viewed through the lenses of history, game theory and market structure, detailed in chief risk officer Ben Hunt’s acclaimed Epsilon Theory newsletter and the FWD Thinking blog.


Read more






Community
Salient is committed to making a positive social impact and is proud to be among the first asset management firms to join the Pledge 1% movement that helps improve and empower communities through philanthropy.


Read more










The New Design
Salient partnered with award-winning design firm Moving Brands to create the visual identity.
Moving Brands captured Salient and Forward’s unique perspectives through a new aesthetic. The colors, eggplant and teal, push the traditional asset management firm palette in a cutting-edge direction. The design is consistent with our precise, measured approach to portfolio construction. The three dimensional logo, a stylized “S”, symbolizes Salient’s capacity to analyze and interpret multiple scenarios simultaneously.
Please continue to visit the existing Salient and Forward websites. Look for a new, unified site in the coming months.











